OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778716978
OL,3,CTed Lasso star Cristo Fernandez signs
OL,4,Cprofessional football deal with US team
OL,6,FTed Lasso star Cristo Fernandez has
OL,7,Fjoined a US football team after
OL,8,Fimpressing them on a trial.
OL,10,FThe 35-year-old, who played AFC
OL,11,FRichmond striker Dani Rojas in the hit
OL,12,FApple TV comedy series, has spent the
OL,13,Flast two months with the football
OL,14,Fteam, El Paso Locomotive, and earned
OL,15,Fhimself a professional contract.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
