OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778716978
OL,3,CTed Lasso star Cristo Fernandez signs
OL,4,Cprofessional football deal with US team
OL,6,FAfter signing an undisclosed deal,
OL,7,FFernandez from Mexico, told his new
OL,8,Fclub's website: "Football has always
OL,9,Fbeen a huge part of my life and
OL,10,Fidentity, and no matter where life has
OL,11,Ftaken me, the dream of competing
OL,12,Fprofessionally never truly left my
OL,13,Fheart.
OL,15,F"I'm incredibly grateful to El Paso
OL,16,FLocomotive FC ` the club, coaches,
OL,17,Fstaff, and especially my team-mates `
OL,18,Ffor opening the doors and giving me
OL,19,Fthe opportunity to compete from day
OL,20,Fone.
