PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778716978
OL,3,CTed Lasso star Cristo Fernandez signs
OL,4,Cprofessional football deal with US team
OL,6,F"This journey back to professional
OL,7,Fsoccer is about believing in yourself,
OL,8,Ftaking risks, and continuing to chase
OL,9,Fyour dreams no matter how unexpected
OL,10,Fthe path may be.
OL,12,F"Maybe I'm just a crazy man with crazy
OL,13,Fdreams...so being here with the
OL,14,F'Locos' actually makes perfect sense."
OL,16,FFernandez previously saw a promising
OL,17,Ffootball career shortened by a knee
OL,18,Finjury when he was 15 years old.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
