OL,3,CTed Lasso star Cristo Fernandez signs
OL,4,Cprofessional football deal with US team
OL,6,FEl Paso Locomotive currently sit
OL,7,Ffourth in the USL Championship - a
OL,8,Ffootball league - after losing three
OL,9,Fof their last four matches following
OL,10,Fan unbeaten start.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FSitcom Ted Lasso follows the story of
OL,18,Fan American football coach who is
OL,19,Fhired to manage a struggling English
OL,20,Ffootball team, AFC Richmond, in west
OL,21,FLondon.
