OL,3,CTed Lasso star Cristo Fernandez signs
OL,4,Cprofessional football deal with US team
OL,6,FThe show features Hannah Waddingham as
OL,7,Fthe club owner, Brett Goldstein as
OL,8,Ffootball star turned coach Roy Kent,
OL,9,Fand Juno Temple.
OL,11,FComedian and actor Goldstein
OL,12,Fcelebrated Fernandez's new sporting
OL,13,Frole with a post on Instagram stories,
OL,14,Fincluding a screenshot of a news
OL,15,Farticle alongside the caption
OL,16,F"yeeeeeeeeeeeeeeaaaaahhhhhhhh!".
OL,18,FSeries four of Ted Lasso is set to
OL,19,Fpremiere on Apple TV in August.
